FBIS4-18282 "drweu063_i_94007" FBIS-WEU-94-063 Daily Report 31 Mar 1994 FRANCE Reactor Explosion Injures 4; No Leak Reported Reactor Explosion Injures 4; No Leak Reported AU3103180194 Paris AFP in English 1751 GMT 31 Mar 94 AU3103180194 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Marseille, France, March 31 (AFP) -- An explosion Thursday [31 March] at a nuclear research center in southern France left four people injured but there was no radiation leak, officials said. They said the explosion occurred in a building where an ageing experimental nuclear reactor was being taken apart. There was no danger of radioactive contamination, they added.
